00:31:25,800 --> 00:31:28,560
I'm afraid I will disappoint you.

588
00:31:29,640 --> 00:31:30,560
Since you're busy,

589
00:31:31,040 --> 00:31:32,920
I'll give you 24 hours

590
00:31:33,160 --> 00:31:33,920
