606
00:32:01,760 --> 00:32:02,239
Come here.

607
00:32:05,479 --> 00:32:06,520
Come on. This way.

608
00:32:08,319 --> 00:32:08,920
Here we are.

609
00:32:22,359 --> 00:32:29,839
Five, four, three, two, one. Happy new year!

610
00:32:52,040 --> 00:32:52,680
Director Xu.

611
00:32:54,199 --> 00:32:55,959
This is the only thing my mother left me

612
00:32:57,760 --> 00:32:59,959
